Job Description:

Exorigos is a dynamic online marketing company that developed its data-driven content platform that specializes in developing innovative technology to effectively connect quality brands to their desired audiences.




We are seeking a skilled and experienced Website Developer with strong backgrounds in both WordPress and JavaScript to join our growing team. The successful candidate will be responsible for designing and developing custom websites and applications using both platforms, as well as maintaining and updating existing websites to ensure they remain functional and visually appealing.




Responsibilities:

 Design and develop custom WordPress websites and applications from start to finish;

 Maintain and update existing WordPress websites to ensure they are functional and up-to-date;

 Collaborate with designers and clients to determine project requirements and deliverables;

 Integrate custom plugins and functions as needed;

 Develop custom JavaScript applications and integrations;

 Troubleshoot and resolve technical issues as they arise;

 Stay up-to-date with the latest WordPress and web development trends and technologies.




Requirements:

 2+ years of professional experience in WordPress and JavaScript development;

 Proficiency in HTML, CSS, PHP, and JavaScript;

 Experience with custom plugin development and theme customization in WordPress;

 Strong attention to detail and ability to work independently;

 Excellent communication skills and the ability to work effectively in a team environment;

 Experience with version control systems (e.g. Git) is a plus.




If you have a passion for web development and are skilled in both WordPress and JavaScript, we encourage you to apply for this exciting opportunity. We offer a dynamic and flexible work environment, as well as on-going training and professional development opportunities.
